I specialise in Front-end HTML/CSS/JS, Back-end PHP/MySQL, WordPress & Laravel development.

I have worked with a vast array of clients including: JLEC, BMCE, Nixly, CNRS, CGI, Capgemini, and International Olympic Committee.

work.summary: Building a PaaS (Platform as a Service)  for IoT using the framework Django and HBase. Architect and scale the data analytics platform. Comprehensive database management using OpenERP. Creating automation for ingesting and serving data to / from our users. Creating prediction models. Using machine learning to build a recomendation engine.

Design and implementation of a database for the needs of the research centres according to the specifications defined. Development of a web platform to facilitate data storage with a general and engines several criteria. Participation in the acceptance phase after the development of the solution.
